note inverted-triangle.vrb — inverted left-aligned right triangle.
note Row 1 prints n stars, last row prints 1 star.

ask the user "how many rows?" and save to rows.

row = rows.
while row >= 1:
    col = 1.
    while col <= row:
        display "*".
        col += 1.
    end.
    say.
    row -= 1.
end.
